# Implementation Plan - Phase 26.1: Fixing Live Screen (Presentation) Issues

This plan addresses several issues with the extended live screen projection:
1.  **Full Screen Mode:** The projected window currently only maximizes; it should be in true full-screen mode (slideshow style) without a title bar or system taskbar.
2.  **Initial Content & Settings Sync:** The projected window is blank initially. Furthermore, even when slides change, the Monitor 2 preset settings (background, typography, alignment, etc.) are not applied because the sub-window only receives a `presetId` but lacks the logic to load or apply those settings.
3.  **Button Lifecycle:** The "Launch" button should transition to "Stop" while active, and "Re-Launch" after being stopped or closed.

## Proposed Changes

### Native (Windows)

#### [MODIFY] [flutter_window.cpp](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/windows/runner/flutter_window.cpp)
- Update `move_subwindow_to_display` logic to:
    - Remove window styles (`WS_CAPTION`, `WS_THICKFRAME`) to hide the title bar and borders.
    - Remove extended styles (`WS_EX_DLGMODALFRAME`, etc.).
    - Use `SetWindowPos` with `SWP_FRAMECHANGED` to apply styles and cover the full screen area (including taskbar).

### Features: Presentation Settings

#### [MODIFY] [presentation_settings.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/settings/data/presentation_settings.dart)
- Add a `toMap()` method to `PresentationSettings` to facilitate passing settings to the sub-window.
- Add a `fromMap()` factory or static method to recreate the object from a Map.

### Features: Projection Logic

#### [MODIFY] [projection_provider.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/settings/presentation/projection_provider.dart)
- Add `hasLaunchedOnce` to `ProjectionState` to track if we should show "RE-LAUNCH".
- Update `launchMonitor2()`:
    - Accept `initialText`, `initialTitle`, `isSong`, and `settingsMap`.
    - Pass these in the initial window arguments.
- Add `stopMonitor2()`:
    - Close the sub-window programmatically using `WindowController.close()`.
    - Reset `monitor2WindowId` and set `hasLaunchedOnce = true`.
- Update `updateMonitor2Preset()`:
    - Fetch the full `PresentationSettings` object.
    - Send the full settings map to the sub-window via `update_preset` method call.

### Main App & Projector Entry Point

#### [MODIFY] [main.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/main.dart)
- Update `_ProjectorAppState`:
    - In `_initWindow`, parse `text`, `title`, `isSong`, and `settings` from arguments.
    - In the method handler, handle `update_preset` by updating the full `_settings` object using `fromMap`.

### Features: Live Controller UI

#### [MODIFY] [live_projector_pane.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/live_controller/presentation/widgets/live_projector_pane.dart)
- Update the "Launch" button:
    - Logic: `isActive ? 'STOP' : (state.hasLaunchedOnce ? 'RE-LAUNCH' : 'LAUNCH')`.
